scouter rip-off? It pisses me off!

245
00:18:04,370 --> 00:18:10,950
You defeated me, the perfect form, after
I took in every cell and powered up.

246
00:18:10,950 --> 00:18:14,200
Your attack deserves to be rewarded.

247
00:18:14,200 --> 00:18:17,320
As you wish, I'll give you my balls.

248
00:18:21,850 --> 00:18:22,960
Take these.

249
00:18:22,960 --> 00:18:26,670
You hid these in there?!
They're disgusting and dirty!

250
00:18:27,510 --> 00:18:34,640
Use these balls to summon the dragon
and make a wish for me.

251
00:18:35,180 --> 00:18:36,990
My wish is

252
00:18:36,990 --> 00:18:39,560
"To graduate from being a virgin..."

253
00:18:39,560 --> 00:18:42,350
Why are you making it sound like
I'm helping you grant your wish?!

254
00:18:42,350 --> 00:18:45,650
And why did you make
such a useless wish?!

255
00:18:46,490 --> 00:18:49,590
Anyway, now that I've collected
all seven balls.

256
00:18:49,590 --> 00:18:52,830
Hurry up and revive Grillin
so I can smoke a cigarette!

257
00:18:52,830 --> 00:18:55,110
What's this? Can I eat this?

258
00:18:55,110 --> 00:18:59,620
There's no way you can eat that disgusting
thing! What about Grillin?

259
00:18:59,620 --> 00:19:00,700
Oh, that's right!

260
00:19:00,700 --> 00:19:03,530
Hurry up and summon the dragon
so it can revive Grillin!

261
00:19:04,360 --> 00:19:08,500
Come out Ooey-gooey Dragon!
Please make my wish come true!

262
00:19:11,850 --> 00:19:13,280
...Huh?

263
00:19:13,280 --> 00:19:16,980
Nothing happened. There're seven
balls all together. What's going on?

264
00:19:18,730 --> 00:19:22,220
Oh? Taking a closer look, this one
isn't an Ooey-gooey ball at all!

265
00:19:22,220 --> 00:19:23,210
What?

266
00:19:23,210 --> 00:19:27,980
The other six balls are real Ooey-gooey
balls. But this one is...

267
00:19:28,560 --> 00:19:29,920
...a Sticky-icky ball!

268
00:19:29,920 --> 00:19:31,450
It's pretty much the same!

269
00:19:31,450 --> 00:19:33,550
What's the difference between
that and an Ooey-gooey ball?!

270
00:19:33,550 --> 00:19:35,510
Yo. It's a Sticky-icky ball!

271
00:19:35,510 --> 00:19:37,750
That's just a technicality!

272
00:19:39,960 --> 00:19:41,970
See?! Something is coming out!

273
00:19:41,970 --> 00:19:44,490
They're all Ooey-gooey balls, after all.

274
00:19:52,550 --> 00:19:56,180
Great job in collecting all
the Slimy-grimy balls.

275
00:19:56,180 --> 00:19:58,430
It's not Ooey-gooey, nor Sticky-icky!

276
00:19:58,430 --> 00:20:02,420
That's the least of our problems.
Hey, hurry up and save Grillin.

277
00:20:02,420 --> 00:20:06,440
I see. It's not Ooey-gooey.
Then I don't care.

278
00:20:06,440 --> 00:20:09,700
Why?! How much loyalty do
you have for Ooey-gooey?!

279
00:20:09,700 --> 00:20:11,930
How badly do you want to
make Grillin Ooey-gooey?!

280
00:20:11,930 --> 00:20:15,550
Just ask him! It doesn't matter
if he's Slimy-grimy!

281
00:20:15,550 --> 00:20:16,760
He's your friend, right?

282
00:20:16,760 --> 00:20:18,810
If it's Slimy-grimy, I prefer
something else.

283
00:20:18,810 --> 00:20:20,400
What do you mean, something else?

284
00:20:24,690 --> 00:20:26,990
Give me some gal's panties!

285
00:20:24,690 --> 00:20:26,990
[Note: A famous line from Dragon Ball when they
first met Shen Long, the dragon.]

286
00:20:26,990 --> 00:20:28,190
Hey!

287
00:20:28,190 --> 00:20:30,560
A gal's Slimy-grimy panties?!

288
00:20:30,560 --> 00:20:32,730
That's such a gross wish!

289
00:20:32,730 --> 00:20:35,400
Don't request a pair of dirty panties
and give up your friend!

290
00:20:35,400 --> 00:20:37,020
Never mind! Forget it!

291
00:20:37,020 --> 00:20:42,550
Hurry up. Or the Slimy-grimy will dry up.

292
00:20:42,550 --> 00:20:43,730
Wait! Hold on a second!

293
00:20:44,650 --> 00:20:47,620
If I have a Slimy-grimy cigarette,
I can't smoke it.

294
00:20:47,620 --> 00:20:49,750
What should I wish for?

295
00:20:49,750 --> 00:20:52,750
I'm about to dry up!

296
00:20:54,340 --> 00:20:55,620
I know!

297
00:20:56,890 --> 00:20:59,260
I'll get the last one.

298
00:21:06,260 --> 00:21:07,930
You're...

299
00:21:09,350 --> 00:21:11,160
Why are you here again?

300
00:21:11,160 --> 00:21:17,570
I've changed my mind...
I want the last cigarette.

301
00:21:19,510 --> 00:21:23,010
I know that's an important memento
from your dad. But...

302
00:21:26,130 --> 00:21:30,820
...you don't need a memento anymore
if you have your dad back.

303
00:21:31,920 --> 00:21:35,030
Don't tell me... Da...

304
00:21:36,200 --> 00:21:38,230
Yeah. It's your dad.

305
00:21:39,810 --> 00:21:41,540
Whose dad is he?!

306
00:21:41,540 --> 00:21:42,850
What's with this Ooey-gooey?!

307
00:21:42,850 --> 00:21:45,050
No, it's not Ooey-gooey, it's Slimy-grimy!

308
00:21:45,050 --> 00:21:47,670
There's a limit to disgracing the dead!

309
00:21:47,670 --> 00:21:51,830
No, it's true. Even if it's
Slimy-grimy, he's real...

310
00:21:57,090 --> 00:21:59,270
It's you again.

311
00:21:59,270 --> 00:22:00,910
Were you able to smoke
a cigarette, after all?

312
00:22:00,910 --> 00:22:02,840
Where will you go next?

313
00:22:04,830 --> 00:22:06,600
I've decided...

314
00:22:08,710 --> 00:22:10,920
...to quit smoking.

315
00:23:48,660 --> 00:23:51,340
After Hijikata returned to earth,

316
00:23:51,340 --> 00:23:55,030
he wasn't able to give
up smoking, after all.

317
00:23:55,030 --> 00:24:01,940
In order to get the legendary cigarette,
Hijikata works hard at training.

318
00:24:01,940 --> 00:24:05,380
And a new powerful enemy appears before him.

319
00:24:06,130 --> 00:24:09,830
Next episode will be Ooey-gooey
ball, episode 120.

320
00:24:09,830 --> 00:24:11,760
Cut it out! This can't be right!

321
00:24:11,760 --> 00:24:13,720
[Note: Parody of next week
remark from Dragon Ball.]

322
00:24:11,760 --> 00:24:13,720
Everyone! Please watch it!

323
00:24:13,720 --> 00:24:14,850
I said, shut up!

324
00:24:15,060 --> 00:24:25,270
[Preview]

325
00:24:16,290 --> 00:24:19,280
Oh, good for you, Hasegawa-san.

326
00:24:19,280 --> 00:24:23,220
I heard you'll head up the conveyor belt sushi
restaurant all by yourself, after all.

327
00:24:23,870 --> 00:24:26,520
The next episode... "Once you've chosen
a dish, you can't give it back."

328
00:24:26,520 --> 00:24:28,780
Have some sushi!

329
00:24:30,060 --> 00:24:34,890
[Actually, there'll be two episodes next week. The other episode... "Japanese Restaurants Abroad Taste Pretty Much like School Cafeteria Lunches"]

330
00:24:34,890 --> 00:24:40,020
[The plan is to sneak into an Amanto restaurant,
